I"^<p><em>Jekyll Theme Simple Blog</em> is a Jekyll theme for GitLab and GitHub Pages. It is based on the nice Cayman Blog theme from the same author. It has everything you need to start blogging like a hacker, today.</p>

<p>Features:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Blog</li>
  <li>Responsive</li>
  <li>Minimal</li>
  <li>Multi-language</li>
  <li>SEO optimized for Facebook preview</li>
  <li>Facebook plugins integration (Page, Comments, Messenger, Like)</li>
  <li>Facebook Mirring Comments</li>
  <li>Social buttons (facebook, instagram, linkedin, twitter, github, gitlab)</li>
  <li>RSS feed multi-language</li>
</ul>
